Package matrix.reconstructionStrategy

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MatrixReconstructionStrategy
    Defines the interface of a function that maps the results of executing each ITask in a job (as defined in AdapterDistribution.createJob(int, Matrix, MatrixReconstructionStrategy)) into a single matrix.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LaplacianMatrixReconstructionStrategy
    This class defines the reconstruction strategy for the laplacian operation.
    RowMatrixReconstructionStrategy
    Defines per row reconstruction strategy used in the following operations.
